    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0763c21"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date><ref type="place" target="#PL000000028939">南嶽石頭山</ref><persName key="A010291">希遷</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0763c22"/><persName key="A010291">釋希遷</persName>，姓陳氏，<placeName key="PL000000031099">端州高<anchor xml:id="beg0763004"/>安<anchor xml:id="end0763004"/></placeName>人也。母方懷孕，<lb
ed="T" n="0763c23"/>不喜葷血。及生岐嶷，雖在孩提，不煩保<lb
ed="T" n="0763c24"/>母。既冠，然諾自許，未嘗以氣色忤人。其鄉<lb
ed="T" n="0763c25"/>洞獠，民畏鬼神，多淫祀，率以牛酒，祚作聖<lb
ed="T" n="0763c26"/>望。<persName key="A010291">遷</persName>輒往毀叢祠，奪牛而歸。歲盈數<anchor xml:id="beg0763005"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>千</sic><corr>十</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0763005"/>，<lb
ed="T" n="0763c27"/>鄉老不能禁其理焉。聞<persName key="A001719">大鑒禪師</persName>南來，學<lb
ed="T" n="0763c28"/>心相踵。<persName key="A010291">遷</persName>乃直往，<persName key="A001719">大鑒</persName>衎然持<anchor xml:id="beg0763006"/>其手<anchor xml:id="end0763006"/>，且戲<lb
ed="T" n="0763c29"/><ref type="person" target="#A010291">之</ref>曰：「苟為<ref type="person" target="#A001719">我</ref>弟子，當肖。」<persName key="A010291">遷</persName>逌爾而笑曰：「諾。」<pb ed="T" n="0764a" xml:id="T50.2061.0764a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0764a01"/>既而靈機一發，廓若初霽。自是上下<placeName key="PL000000031276">羅浮</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0764a02"/>往來<placeName key="PL000000000078">三峽</placeName>間。<date from-iso="0728-02-19" key="j19870051987358" to-iso="0729-02-06">開元十六年</date>，<placeName key="PL000000031276">羅浮</placeName>受具戒，<date from-iso="0728-02-19" key="j19870051987358" to-iso="0729-02-06">是年</date><lb
ed="T" n="0764a03"/>歸就山，夢與<persName key="A001719">大鑒</persName>同乘一龜，泳於深池。覺<lb
ed="T" n="0764a04"/>而占曰：「龜是靈智也，池是性海也。<ref type="person" target="#A010291">吾</ref>與<ref type="person" target="#A001719">師</ref>乘<lb
ed="T" n="0764a05"/>靈智遊性海久矣，又何夢邪？」後聞<placeName key="PL000000019385">廬陵清<lb
ed="T" n="0764a06"/>涼山</placeName><ptr target="#n1155"/><persName key="A003666">思禪師</persName>為<persName key="A001719">曹溪</persName>補處，又攝衣從<ref type="person" target="#A003666">之</ref>。當<lb
ed="T" n="0764a07"/>時<persName key="A003666">思公</persName>之門，學者麏至。及<persName key="A010291">遷</persName>之來，乃曰：「角雖<lb
ed="T" n="0764a08"/>多，一麟足矣。」<date from-iso="0742" key="j19921141993438" to-iso="0745">天寶初</date>，始造<placeName key="PL000000028939">衡山南寺</placeName><note resp="sgsz">《石門文字禪．次韻游南臺寺》：「青原生下一角麟，單丁住山須底物。」明此為<placeName key="PL000000028939">南臺寺</placeName>無誤。 (cf. 石門文字禪<ref>CBETA, J23, no. B135, p. 605, b13</ref>)</note>。<ref type="place" target="#PL000000028939">寺</ref>之東<lb
ed="T" n="0764a09"/>有石狀如臺，乃結庵其上，杼載絕岳，眾仰<lb
ed="T" n="0764a10"/>之，號曰<persName key="A010291">石頭和尚</persName>焉。初，<placeName key="PL000000028928">嶽</placeName>中有<persName key="A010293">固</persName>、<persName key="A010199">瓚</persName>、<persName key="A004015">讓</persName>三<lb
ed="T" n="0764a11"/>禪師，皆<persName key="A001719">曹溪</persName>門下，僉謂其徒曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010291">彼石頭</ref>真<lb
ed="T" n="0764a12"/>師子吼，必能使汝眼清涼。」由是門人歸慕<lb
ed="T" n="0764a13"/><anchor xml:id="beg0764sgsz1"/>焉<anchor xml:id="end0764sgsz1"/>。或問解脫，曰：「誰能縛汝？」問淨土，曰：「誰能<lb
ed="T" n="0764a14"/>垢汝？」其答對簡速，皆此類也。<date from-iso="0764-02-11" key="j20001462000499" to-iso="0765-01-29">廣德二年</date>，門人<lb
ed="T" n="0764a15"/>請下于<placeName key="PL000000028665">梁端</placeName><note resp="sgsz">《景德傳燈錄》：「<placeName key="PL000000028665">潭州</placeName>招提<persName key="A010296">慧朗禪師</persName>……後住梁端招提寺。」疑「<placeName key="PL000000028665">潭州</placeName>」當時又稱「<placeName key="PL000000028665">梁端</placeName>」。一說 「梁端」指山頂。宋王安石《俞秀老忽然不見》詩：「忽去飄然遊冶盤，共疑策杖在梁端。」 (cf. 景德傳燈錄<ref>CBETA, T51, no. 2076, p. 311, b08</ref>)</note>。自<placeName key="PL000000018627">江西</placeName>主<persName key="A003623">大寂</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000028665">湖南</placeName>主<persName key="A010291">石頭</persName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0764a16"/>往來憧憧，不見<ref type="person" target="#A003623 #A010291">二大士</ref>為無知矣。<date key="j20100032010003" when-iso="0791-02-06">貞元六<lb
ed="T" n="0764a17"/>年庚午歲十二月二十五日</date>順化，春秋九十<lb
ed="T" n="0764a18"/>一，僧臘六十三。門人<persName key="A010296">慧朗</persName>、<persName key="A010297">振朗</persName>、<persName key="A010298">波利</persName>、<persName key="A010299">道悟</persName>、<persName key="A010301">道<lb
ed="T" n="0764a19"/>銑</persName>、<persName key="A010302">智舟</persName>相與建塔于東嶺。<ref type="date" target="#j20209252021289">塔成三十載</ref>，國子<lb
ed="T" n="0764a20"/>博士<persName key="A010303">劉軻</persName>素明玄理，欽尚祖風，與<persName key="A010301">道銑</persName>相<lb
ed="T" n="0764a21"/>遇，盛述<ref type="person" target="#A010291">先師</ref>之道。<persName key="A010303">軻</persName>追仰前烈，為碑紀德，<lb
ed="T" n="0764a22"/><date from-iso="0821" key="j20209682022078" to-iso="0824">長慶</date>中也。勅諡<persName key="A010291">無際大師</persName>，塔曰見相焉。</p>
